{"tid":2047763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律政司：會研究是否跟進黃大仙男子脫暴動罪 ( 係跟進 唔係上訴 釘你第二條)","createTime":"2020-06-02T10:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T12:10:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1e831684a32eabbbb229ebc368ca64e949e551cc","tid":2047763,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"律政司：會研究是否跟進黃大仙男子脫暴動罪<br />\n02.06.2020 18:14<br />\n<br />\n去年10月1日涉參與包圍黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍的20歲男子林子浩，下午在區域法院被裁定暴動罪不成立，獲當庭釋放。律政司表示，會研究法官的判決理據和主控官的報告，決定是否需要跟進。<br />\n<br />\n法官沈小民在庭上指，控方兩名警員的供詞，未能解釋被告被制服後頭破血流的原因；法官又指，警方在基協中學門外制服被告，但警員沒向校方索取閉路電視呈堂，警員供詞又指追捕時視線清晰，但辯方呈上的影片顯示，當時有消防車橫放路面，因此不能夠安心接納兩名警員的供詞，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297600&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1297600%26csid%3D261_341&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=06c8adcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297600&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"224c33d444e3c51a8bb769fd4df4efc7f0dc3a83","tid":2047763,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"販毒少女唔研究下?"},{"pid":"5716c9ea9458396c3ee4bd730569390c7b4b275a","tid":2047763,"uid":3860,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:25:01.000Z","msg":"屌你唔跟進D狗作假口供?"},{"pid":"0ac41f839e60a35a2c5b9346500c0ead4357c66a","tid":2047763,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"刑事檢控專員梁卓然又發狗瘟亂咬人"},{"pid":"33571c526ca5215aeb7aacd57983d1053139b885","tid":2047763,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5716c9ea9458396c3ee4bd730569390c7b4b275a","tid":2047763,"uid":3860,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:25:01.000Z","msg":"屌你唔跟進D狗作假口供?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:26:0